Package org.lukep.javavis.program.java

Class Summary
JavaCodePostProcessor Runs post-processing actions on the abstract program model tree.
JavaCodeProcessor The JavaCodeProcessor is an AbstractProcessor that is utilised by Javac to call up when it's time to scan a bunch of parsed root compilation unit nodes.
JavaCodeTreeVisitor The Class JavaCodeTreeVisitor.
JavaSourceLoaderThread Following the construction of a list of "compilation units", the JavaSourceLoaderThread adds a custom JavaCodeProcessor (an implementation of AbstractProcessor) to the compiler’s CompilationTask.
